According to our analysis,

517
00:27:45,970 --> 00:27:48,640
the mercury rate was 20 times higher
than the standard rate.

518
00:27:49,140 --> 00:27:51,570
The victim was poisoned by mercury
at this place.

519
00:27:51,569 --> 00:27:54,309
Did someone order him
to go in there?

520
00:27:54,309 --> 00:27:57,379
It's his fault for going inside
an abandoned building.

521
00:27:57,650 --> 00:27:59,350
Yes, it's his fault.

522
00:27:59,350 --> 00:28:03,020
But building a temporary dorm
at a place with potential risk...

523
00:28:03,019 --> 00:28:05,959
and not taking any safety measures
whatsoever...

524
00:28:06,059 --> 00:28:08,189
is the responsibility
of the company.

525
00:28:08,190 --> 00:28:10,060
That doesn't make sense.

526
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:12,800
How much do we have to take
responsibility for?

527
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:15,970
Goodness, this is just because
of their hobby.

528
00:28:15,970 --> 00:28:17,470
Do you take us for fools?

529
00:28:17,470 --> 00:28:19,400
Do you think we're some
volunteer group?

530
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:21,970
Please quiet down.
Let's have some order.

531
00:28:22,970 --> 00:28:24,310
The analysis result...

532
00:28:24,710 --> 00:28:26,780
for cross-checking is the same.

533
00:28:27,380 --> 00:28:30,380
Then let's begin the vote.

534
00:28:37,390 --> 00:28:39,690
(Chairman of Committee,
Park Hyun Sung)

535
00:28:44,430 --> 00:28:46,830
