of the votes.

536
00:28:48,499 --> 00:28:50,069
Those who agree, five votes.

537
00:28:50,069 --> 00:28:51,369
Those who disagree, four votes.

538
00:28:51,370 --> 00:28:53,270
It has been voted as work-related.

539
00:28:53,269 --> 00:28:57,209
The decision's been made that
TL Metro is responsible.

540
00:28:57,569 --> 00:29:01,179
What is this? This is nothing but
unfair treatment of companies.

541
00:29:01,479 --> 00:29:04,049
Will you let everyone apply for
industrial accidents now?

542
00:29:04,049 --> 00:29:06,749
- This is ridiculous.
- All right, then.

543
00:29:06,749 --> 00:29:09,289
Great job, everyone. Thank you.

544
00:29:09,289 --> 00:29:11,489
Chairman Park, thank you.

545
00:29:11,489 --> 00:29:13,089
Let's wrap it up now.
